sections.History:
===''[[Game of Thrones: A Telltale Games Series]]''===
====&quot;[[The Lost Lords]]&quot;====
If [[Gared Tuttle]] chooses to tell [[Jon Snow]] that he intends to find the [[North Grove]], Jon will laugh and say that [[Old Nan]] used to tell him and his half-siblings a tale about it that featured ice dragons and trees as tall as the sky.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[The Lost Lords]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;

====&quot;[[The Sword in the Darkness]]&quot;====
[[Duncan Tuttle]] delivers some [[ironwood]] to [[Castle Black]] and gives his nephew Gared a map that belonged to Lord [[Gregor Forrester]] that seems to show how to find the North Grove. Gregor has written on the map that the North Grove is located &quot;beneath the watchful eye of the Ice Dragon&quot;.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[The Sword in the Darkness]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;
